-- Standard acte models (MVP §10: succession + donation, Droit de la famille).
-- Authored as Tiptap JSON (see frontend/src/admin/trames/editor) with 'champ' inline
-- nodes for fields that auto-populate from the dossier/personnes ({{ field }} in the
-- generated .docx) or are left for the rédacteur to fill in manually per dossier.
-- Multi-party lists (comparants, héritiers, biens) are 'manuel' fields: the trame
-- content model doesn't support Jinja loops yet, only flat variables per section.

